" الممكنة."

#: ../../source/3DNuclei/Nuclei3DTimeConsumingPipeline.md:268
msgid "**MeasureObjectSizeShape module**"
msgstr "**وحدة قياس حجم وشكل الكائن**"

#: ../../source/3DNuclei/Nuclei3DTimeConsumingPipeline.md:270
